Localization.Name: Ripper SMG
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Unknown
Item Type: SMG
Class: Energy (Laser)

Battery Size: 60
Rate Of Fire: 800 rpm
Effective Range: 30 m

Scrapped together from whatever parts and pieces were available, the Ripper SMG can probably do enough damage to get you out of a tight spot. Just be ready for things to get messy.
